Divine Tithes

Tithes let you offer coins to Mitra, Gaea, or Set. They can push the hidden
divine pressure of the world and may earn favor when you tithe to your own
patron.

Commands:

  tithe <amount> to <mitra|gaea|set>
  tithe <mitra|gaea|set> <amount>
  tithe <amount> at shrine

Tithes also tug your alignment and ethics toward the god you honor. The omens
command describes the public result without showing raw pressure numbers.

Related help:

